@CalebtheHedgehog 

I recall from some Sonic comic I had when I was a kid Robotnik was once a good guy, not fat and using the chaos emeralds for the cause of good. Before he turned evil, Sonic was born through a freak accident with his experiments and eventually he fused himself with a rotten egg, turning him into the fat bastard Eggman we know today.

If I recall correctly he named himself Ovi Kintobor before the accident, wich obviously is his named spelled backwards.
